*&quot;Hippeastrum calyptratum&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum canterai&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum correiense&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum cybister&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum evansiae&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum ferreyrae&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum iguazuanum&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum leopoldii&quot; 
*&quot;Hippeastrum miniatum&quot; 
